<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>Contact Us</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="CSS/Contact_Us.css">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="IMG/spirals.png">
</head>
<body>
<div class="head-bar">
    <%- include('./layout/NavBar') %>
</div>
<div class="header-container">
    <div class="img-container">
        <div class="text-overlay">
            <h1>
                Contact Us
                <br>
                <span style="font-size: 25px">Let us help you explore what you love</span>
            </h1>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 d-flex align-items-stretch">
            <div class="Contact LeftContact">
                <p>We appreciate your interest in our historical monument destination and are here to assist you with
                    any
                    inquiries or feedback you may have.</p>
                <p>We also value your feedback and suggestions so please feel free to reach out to us using the contact
                    details
                    provided below.</p>
                <p class="text">
                    <i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i> Số 8A Tôn Thất Thuyết, Mỹ Đình, Nam Từ Liêm<br>
                    <i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i> Hà Nội, Việt Nam<br>
                    <i class="fa fa-phone-square"></i> <a href="tel:0123456789">0123456789</a><br>
                    <i class="fa fa-envelope"></i> <a href="mailto:dtranjack@gmail.com">dtranjack@gmail.com</a>
                </p>
                <div class="map">
                    <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d8481.902586661165!2d105.78030173056202!3d21.02908408821946!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3135ab86cece9ac1%3A0xa9bc04e04602dd85!2zRlBUIEFwdGVjaCBIw6AgTuG7mWkgLSBI4buHIFRo4buRbmcgxJDDoG8gVOG6oW8gTOG6rXAgVHLDrG5oIFZpw6puIFF14buRYyBU4bq_IChTaW5jZSAxOTk5KQ!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1688212310420!5m2!1svi!2s"
                            width="100%" height="100%" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy"
                            referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 d-flex align-items-stretch" id="comform">
            <div class="Contact RightContact">
                <p>You can also use the contact form on this page to send us a message directly. We strive to
                    respond to all inquiries promptly and provide you with the assistance you require.</p>
                <div>
                    <p>Please provide your contact information as well as your questions or feedback; we will get back
                        to
                        you as soon as possible.</p>
                </div>

                <form id="contact-form" method="post" action="/submitContact">
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="full-name" class="form-label">Full Name <span
                                    style="color: red">*</span></label>
                        <input type="text" id="full-name" name="full-name" class="form-control">
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="email" class="form-label">Email Address <span
                                    style="color: red">*</span></label>
                        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="form-control" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="phone" class="form-label">Phone Number</label>
                        <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" class="form-control"
                               placeholder="Ex: (123)-456-789">
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="subj" class="form-label">Choose Subject</label>
                        <select id="subj" name="subject" required class="form-select">
                            <option value="General_Enquiry">General Enquiry</option>
                            <option value="FeedBack">Feedback</option>
                            <option value="Other">Other</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="msg" class="form-label">Message <span style="color: red">*</span></label>
                        <textarea rows="4" id="msg" name="msg" class="form-control"
                                  placeholder="Messages or feedbacks here."></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <input type="submit" value="Submit" class="btn btn-primary">
                    </div>
                </form>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div style="margin-top: 50px" class="footer">
    <%- include('./layout/footer') %>
</div>

<!-- Back to Top button -->
<button id="backToTopBtn" class="btn btn-primary" title="Back to Top">
    <i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i>
</button>

<style>
    #backToTopBtn {
        display: none;
        position: fixed;
        bottom: 20px;
        right: 20px;
        z-index: 99;
    }
</style>

<script>
    // Show/hide "Back to Top" button based on scroll position
    $(window).scroll(function () {
        if ($(this).scrollTop() > 100) {
            $('#backToTopBtn').fadeIn();
        } else {
            $('#backToTopBtn').fadeOut();
        }
    });

    // Smooth scroll to top when the button is clicked (faster animation)
    $('#backToTopBtn').click(function () {
        $('html, body').animate({ scrollTop: 0 }, 300); // Adjust the duration here (in milliseconds)
        return false;
    });
</script>

<script>
    // JavaScript code for parallax scrolling effect
    const headerContainer = document.querySelector('.header-container');
    const imgContainer = headerContainer.querySelector('.img-container');
    const textOverlay = headerContainer.querySelector('.text-overlay');

    window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
        // Calculate the scroll position
        const scrollY = window.scrollY;

        // Adjust the position of the text overlay based on scrollY to create the parallax effect
        textOverlay.style.transform = `translateY(${scrollY * 0.5}px)`;
    });
</script>
<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>